Package org.openscience.cdk.isomorphism

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AtomMappingTools  
    AtomMatcher
    Defines compatibility checking of atoms for (subgraph)-isomorphism mapping.
    BondMatcher
    Defines compatibility checking of bonds for (subgraph)-isomorphism mapping.
    ComponentGrouping
    A predicate for verifying component level grouping in query/target structure matching.
    IsomorphismTester
    A too simplistic implementation of an isomorphism test for chemical graphs.
    Mappings
    A fluent interface for handling (sub)-graph mappings from a query to a target structure.
    Pattern
    A structural pattern for finding an exact matching in a target compound.
    SmartsStereoMatch
    Filters SMARTS matches for those that have valid stereochemistry configuration.
    Ullmann
    A structure pattern which utilises the Ullmann algorithm [Ullmann J R, An Algorithm for Subgraph Isomorphism, Journal of the Association for Computing Machinery, 1976, 23:?-?, doi:10.1145/321921.321925].
    UniversalIsomorphismTester
    This class implements a multipurpose structure comparison tool.
    VentoFoggia
    A structure pattern which utilises the Vento-Foggia (VF) algorithm [Cordella Luigi P and Foggia Pasquale and Carlo Sansone and Vento Mario , A (Sub)Graph Isomorphism Algorithm for Matching Large Graphs, IEEE TRANSACTIONS ON PATTERN ANALYSIS AND MACHINE INTELLIGENCE, 2004, 26:10].
